king angles and deeper detection\nlimits will increase the pace of discovery to ultimately map the demographics,\ncomposition, evolution, and origin of planets spanning a broad range of masses\nand ages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 May 2016 20:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-07"}
