s not lead to the existence of clumped matter on extra small\nscales inside halos for large masses while this possibility exists for masses\n$M\\lesssim 10^{11} M_\\odot$ where the phenomenology of ultra-local models would\nbe most different from $\\Lambda$-CDM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 May 2016 11:01:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 May 2016 13:04:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-17"}
