ons of concepts in the feature selection step lead to a significant\nincrease in the performance of summarization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 May 2016 11:33:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Sep 2016 16:02:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 May 2017 14:37:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
