oned in colorful connected components). We give a fixed-parameter\nalgorithm for MEC paramterized by $k$ and, when the input graph is a tree, we\ngive a poly-kernel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 May 2016 15:55:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 15:14:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-20"}
